{"tid":1957442,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"肺疫危機下 美國首間小型銀行倒閉","createTime":"2020-04-04T02:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T09:43:32.000Z","uid":82340,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"30c18e6beac39e47736aab218acad518c0f20a15","tid":1957442,"uid":82340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:43:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2428051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2428051&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=03a4e7fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2428051</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情爆發以來，美國出現首宗銀行倒閉個案。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦存款保障機構(FDIC)宣布，已經接管位於西弗吉尼亞州的小型銀行The First State Bank of Barboursville。西弗吉尼亞州的金融機構監管部門較早時關閉該銀行。<br />\n<br />\nFirst State Bank旗下有4間分行，集團資產總值為1.52億美元。根據公告，MVB Bank將接管First State Bank的1.395億美元存款，4間分行周一起將易名MVB Bank，冀繼續經營。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2abaf8034180094f0e44d9ec52896cf1e16e39e","tid":1957442,"uid":225916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"美爆 然後支那一齊攬炒"},{"pid":"1a1854838a5f89c73e22f8b2571859a0fab195db","tid":1957442,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cb023ce9c8ffcfa1f25b01b603e38d2efac6e5","tid":1957442,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"甘肅銀行應該已被黨接管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信黨，不怕！"},{"pid":"29612a1f9b16f3b547ef995fa4aef777d2e94dbf","tid":1957442,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2ab